{"title":"hexo-error","date":"2018-12-23T09:14:10.000Z","slug":"hexo-error","categories":["Hexo"],"updated":"2018-12-23T10:43:25.890Z","content":"<h1 id=\"标签和分类不显示\"><a href=\"#标签和分类不显示\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"标签和分类不显示\"></a>标签和分类不显示</h1><p>1.先看下站点的source下是否有tags和categories这两个文件夹，如果没有需要先创建。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo new page &quot;tags&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">$ hexo new page &quot;categories&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>2.一般只需在markdown文章的头部加上下面这两句。注意：冒号后空一格</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">title: ...</span><br><span class=\"line\">date: ...</span><br><span class=\"line\">tags: 标签名  # 添加这一句</span><br><span class=\"line\">categories: 分类名 # 添加这一句</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>3.如果还不行,打开主题的配置文件(_config.yml)，找到menu,看是否正确</p>\n<p>注意：是主题的配置文件！！！</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">menu:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  home: /</span><br><span class=\"line\">  # About: /about</span><br><span class=\"line\">  # Links: /links</span><br><span class=\"line\">  tags: /tags</span><br><span class=\"line\">  categories: /categories</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"hexo-d后-ERROR-Deployer-not-found-git\"><a href=\"#hexo-d后-ERROR-Deployer-not-found-git\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"hexo d后 ERROR Deployer not found: git\"></a>hexo d后 ERROR Deployer not found: git</h1><p>输入下面命令即可</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install --save hexo-deployer-git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"输入github地址无法访问博客\"><a href=\"#输入github地址无法访问博客\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"输入github地址无法访问博客\"></a>输入github地址无法访问博客</h1><p>查看站点配置文件_config.yml</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">deploy:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  type: git</span><br><span class=\"line\">  repository: #这里直接复制https地址或者ssh密钥 </span><br><span class=\"line\">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"如果本地无法访问\"><a href=\"#如果本地无法访问\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"如果本地无法访问\"></a>如果本地无法访问</h1><p>查看站点配置文件_config.yml</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">url: http://yoursite.com</span><br><span class=\"line\">root: /</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>如果放在子目录下</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">url: http://yoursite.com/child</span><br><span class=\"line\">root: /child</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"git常用指令","slug":"git常用指令"},"next":{"title":"搭建博客","slug":"hexo"},"link":"http://yoursite.com/post/hexo-error/","toc":[{"title":"标签和分类不显示","id":"标签和分类不显示","index":"1"},{"title":"hexo d后 ERROR Deployer not found: git","id":"hexo-d后-ERROR-Deployer-not-found-git","index":"2"},{"title":"输入github地址无法访问博客","id":"输入github地址无法访问博客","index":"3"},{"title":"如果本地无法访问","id":"如果本地无法访问","index":"4"}]}